參考書目 References


備註 Remarks
     成績考核
Grading Criteria:
學生自己選擇評定成績方法 Grading selection by a student:
1) 小考平均成績=學期成績Quizes average score = Semester grade
2) 小考平均成績 ÷ 期末考試成績 => 其中校高成績 = 學期成績Quizes average score ÷ Final exam score => Higher score = Semester grade
若無小考平均成績 => 期末考試成績 = 學期成績No quizes average score => Final exam score = Semester grade




基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 厚植人文素養及西洋文學、語言、文化及知識
 To cultivate their spirit of humanity and increase their knowledge of western literature, languages and cultures.
■ 培養獨立思考、團隊合作及思辨能力、發展關懷與服務精神
 To improve their capabilities for independent thinking, teamwork, and critical analysis and develop their civil concern and spirit of service
■ 擴展國際視野、接受多元文化及跨領域學習
 To broaden their global vision and accept diverse cultures and interdisciplinary 
learning.
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 具備人文素養及社會關懷與服務的能力
 Ability to provide social concern and service with a spirit of humanity.
□ 具備語言學、語言教學理論、知識與應用能力
 Ability to apply professionally the knowledge and theory of linguistics and language teaching.
■ 英外語溝通及應用能力
 Ability to demonstrate foreign language proficiency in various applications.
□ 多面向深入閱讀、賞析外國文學、語言、文化與藝術的能力
 Ability to appreciate and analyze foreign literatures, languages and cultures from multi-dimensional perspectives.
■ 適應多元文化與職場領域的知能
 Abiltiy to accomodate diverse cultures and professional fields.
□ 培養獨立及批判性思考、提問及解決問題的能力
 Ability to think independently and critically and to raise questions and solve problems.
 

課程概述 Course Description
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    有限主題範圍以內的俄語口語表達與聽力
Oral communication on the limited scope of topics    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1國籍。民族。 Citizenship and ethnicity.2郵局。外語。 Post-office. Country of living. Foreign languages. 3音樂會。芭蕾舞。 Concerts. Ballet. Festivals.4節日。作客。節日晚會。Visiting friends. Parties.5在外面吃東西。Going out dining.6人生。 Life matters.7職業。未來計畫。Profession and occupation. Planning future.8科學。 Sciences.9寫信。Writing letter.10期中考試。 Mid-term exam11展藍會。Exhibitions.12莫斯科大學。大學。 Moscow state University. Studying at university.13體育。運動。Physical activities, sports.14身體健康。Healthy way of life.15學習外語。Leaning foreign languages.16旅行。參觀。 Travel. Sight-seeing.17俄國旅行。 Travel in Russia.18期末考試。 Final exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


